<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Order Failed</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .order-details {
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .order-details h2 {
      color: #dc3545;
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .order-details p {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cross-mark {
      color: #dc3545;
      font-size: 64px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .btn-retry {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      font-size: 18px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
      background-color: #dc3545;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn-retry:hover {
      background-color: #b21f2d;
    }

    .btn-home {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 200px;
      margin: 20px auto 0;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      font-size: 18px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
      background-color: #007bff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn-home:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="order-details">
      <div class="cross-mark">&#10060;</div>
      <h2>Order Failed</h2>
      <p>We're sorry, but there was an issue with your order. Please try again or contact support if the issue persists.</p>
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary btn-home">Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>